      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 44 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 44 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：包有魚，无咎，不利賓。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject with a wallet of fish. There will be no error. But it will not be well to let (the subject of the first line) go forward to the guests.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
