      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 44 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：臀无膚，其行次且，厲，无大咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows one from whose buttocks the skin has been stripped so that he walks with difficulty. The position is perilous, but there will be no great error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
