      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：以杞包瓜，含章，有隕自天。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, (shows its subject as) a medlar tree overspreading the gourd (beneath it). If he keep his brilliant qualities concealed, (a good issue) will descend (as) from Heaven.</seg>
